author: dmkarr
msg: Removed exception "printStackTrace()" call.  Wrapped each PropertyDescriptor
creation with exception catcher instead of wrapping entire method, so only bad
calls are excluded.  Changed to add entries to ArrayList instead of array to
remove possibility of getting array length or index references incorrect.

author: dmkarr
msg: Fixed performance problem caused by using exception processing for normal
processing flow.  It now will just not call the setter method if the original
expression or resulting value is null.
